OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1782586118
OL,3,CGreater Manchester firefighters
OL,4,Cdeployed to Venezuela after earthquakes
OL,6,FMerseyside firefighters are leading
OL,7,Fthe UK's search and rescue mission to
OL,8,FVenezuela after devastating
OL,9,Fearthquakes, with crews from Greater
OL,10,FManchester also deployed to help save
OL,11,Flives.
OL,13,FThe specialist team is part of a 68-
OL,14,Fstrong UK International Search and
OL,15,FRescue (UK ISAR) deployment sent to
OL,16,Fsupport emergency efforts following
OL,17,Fthis week's deadly earthquakes.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
