OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,364,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1782586118
OL,3,CGreater Manchester firefighters
OL,4,Cdeployed to Venezuela after earthquakes
OL,6,FLed by Merseyside Fire and Rescue
OL,7,FService, the operation brings together
OL,8,Ffirefighters and rescue specialists
OL,9,Ffrom 14 fire and rescue services
OL,10,Facross the UK, including Greater
OL,11,FManchester Fire and Rescue Service
OL,12,F(GMFRS).
OL,14,FThe team departed from RAF Brize
OL,15,FNorton on Friday aboard a Royal Air
OL,16,FForce Voyager aircraft, taking six
OL,17,Fspecialist search dogs, drones capable
OL,18,Fof assessing unstable buildings and
OL,19,Fother rescue equipment to help locate
OL,20,Fsurvivors trapped beneath collapsed
OL,21,Fstructures.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,364,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1782586118
OL,3,CGreater Manchester firefighters
OL,4,Cdeployed to Venezuela after earthquakes
OL,6,FFirefighters deployed from GMFRS
OL,7,Finclude, Watch Manager Gavin Kearsley
OL,8,Ffrom Ashton, Watch Manager Dan Davey
OL,9,Ffrom Bury Training Centre and Watch
OL,10,FManager Mike Hirst from Leigh.
OL,12,FThey are expected to support search
OL,13,Fand rescue efforts for up to 10 days.
OL,15,FMore than 920 people have been killed
OL,16,Fafter 7.2 and 7.5 magnitude quakes
OL,17,Fstruck the country within minutes of
OL,18,Feach other on Wednesday 24 June.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,364,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1782586118
OL,3,CGreater Manchester firefighters
OL,4,Cdeployed to Venezuela after earthquakes
OL,6,FIt is believed that the death toll
OL,7,Ffigure will continue to climb in the
OL,8,Fcoming days, with some 3,360 people
OL,9,Finjured and time running out to find
OL,10,Fsurvivors.
OL,12,FNational Fire Chiefs Council (NFCC)
OL,13,FChair, Phil Garrigan, said: "The
OL,14,Fthoughts of everyone across the UK's
OL,15,Ffire and rescue services are with
OL,16,Fthose affected by the devastating
OL,17,Fearthquakes in Venezuela.
OL,26,@uD@]OU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,364,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1782586118
OL,3,CGreater Manchester firefighters
OL,4,Cdeployed to Venezuela after earthquakes
OL,6,F"In response to a request made through
OL,7,Fthe UK Government, a team of highly
OL,8,Ftrained UK firefighters and specialist
OL,9,Fmedics has been deployed to support
OL,10,Fthe international rescue effort.
OL,12,F"These firefighters bring exceptional
OL,13,Fskill, experience and dedication, and
OL,14,Fwill work alongside local and
OL,15,Finternational teams to provide vital
OL,16,Fsearch and rescue support where it is
OL,17,Fneeded most, with the intent to help
OL,18,Fsave lives in extremely challenging
OL,19,Fconditions.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,364,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1782586118
OL,3,CGreater Manchester firefighters
OL,4,Cdeployed to Venezuela after earthquakes
OL,6,F"Their mission is clear and I know
OL,7,Fthey will respond with focus,
OL,8,Fcompassion and care."
OL,10,FThe deployment forms part of the UK's
OL,11,Fwider humanitarian response, with the
OL,12,FGovernment also announcing an initial
OL,13,F#2 million in emergency funding to
OL,14,Fsupport relief efforts in Venezuela.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,364,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1782586118
OL,3,CGreater Manchester firefighters
OL,4,Cdeployed to Venezuela after earthquakes
OL,6,FPrime Minister Sir Keir Starmer said:
OL,7,F"My thoughts are with the people of
OL,8,FVenezuela following this week's
OL,9,Fdevastating earthquakes. The UK stands
OL,10,Fin solidarity with all those affected,
OL,11,Fparticularly those who have lost loved
OL,12,Fones, homes and livelihoods.
OL,14,F"We are making #2 million of emergency
OL,15,Fhumanitarian funding available and are
OL,16,Fworking closely with international
OL,17,Fpartners to ensure vital support
OL,18,Freaches those most in need as quickly
OL,19,Fas possible."
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOU{D@MO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,364,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1782586118
OL,3,CGreater Manchester firefighters
OL,4,Cdeployed to Venezuela after earthquakes
OL,6,FThe firefighters and rescue
OL,7,Fspecialists are part of the UK's
OL,8,FNational Resilience capability, which
OL,9,Fremains on permanent standby to
OL,10,Frespond to major disasters overseas.
OL,12,FMany of those deploying have
OL,13,Fpreviously taken part in international
OL,14,Frescue operations following the
OL,15,Fearthquakes in Turkiye and Morocco in
OL,16,F2023, where UK teams helped locate and
OL,17,Frescue survivors from collapsed
OL,18,Fbuildings.
OL,26,@wD@Qxz
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,364,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1782586118
OL,3,CGreater Manchester firefighters
OL,4,Cdeployed to Venezuela after earthquakes
OL,6,FForeign Secretary Yvette Cooper said:
OL,7,F"The UK today has sent support to
OL,8,FVenezuela following these devastating
OL,9,Fearthquakes.
OL,11,F"Our specialist search and rescue
OL,12,Fteams are deploying to help save
OL,13,Flives, and we are providing a #2
OL,14,Fmillion package to support the
OL,15,Fhumanitarian response."
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUwD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,364,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1782586118
OL,3,CGreater Manchester firefighters
OL,4,Cdeployed to Venezuela after earthquakes
OL,6,FThe RAF aircraft also carried
OL,7,Fhumanitarian specialists responsible
OL,8,Ffor logistics, security and supply
OL,9,Fchains, while an advance team from the
OL,10,FUK's Emergency Medical Team has
OL,11,Ftravelled to Venezuela to assess
OL,12,Furgent healthcare needs and determine
OL,13,Fwhat further medical support may be
OL,14,Frequired.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,364,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36311
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1782586118
OL,3,CGreater Manchester firefighters
OL,4,Cdeployed to Venezuela after earthquakes
OL,6,FThe Government said the #2 million
OL,7,Fpackage will help fund immediate life-
OL,8,Fsaving assistance and contribute to
OL,9,Fthe wider international response
OL,10,Fthrough organisations including the
OL,11,FRed Cross and United Nations emergency
OL,12,Ffunds.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
